  notes:
    - "Wave 653 (sk3091): __hash__, __eq__, __bool__ dict-presence checks for socket types."
    - "socket.socket is a Python class; it does not define __hash__, __eq__, or __bool__ in its __dict__."
    - "socket.AddressFamily and socket.SocketKind are IntEnum subclasses (EnumType metaclass)."
    - "Neither socket.AddressFamily nor socket.SocketKind defines __hash__, __eq__, or __bool__ in its own __dict__."
    - "All values verified with Python 3.14.4 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-13."
  created_at: "2026-04-13"
error_model: python_exceptions

